OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782865086
OL,3,CDefence Secretary faces questions on
OL,4,C#4.7bn funding gap left to Andy Burnham
OL,6,FDefence Secretary Dan Jarvis is facing
OL,7,Fquestions over a #4.7 billion black
OL,8,Fhole in the plan to raise defence
OL,9,Fspending and whether Andy Burnham was
OL,10,Fblindsided by the need to plug that
OL,11,Fgap in his first budget.
OL,13,FSir Keir Starmer announced #15 billion
OL,14,Fof spending over the next four years
OL,15,Fto support the Defence Investment
OL,16,FPlan, but the Treasury put off setting
OL,17,Fout full details of how it would fund
OL,18,Fthe increase.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782865086
OL,3,CDefence Secretary faces questions on
OL,4,C#4.7bn funding gap left to Andy Burnham
OL,6,FIn a written statement to Parliament,
OL,7,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said only two-
OL,8,Fthirds of the sum ` #10.3 billion `
OL,9,Fhad been identified, while the
OL,10,Fremaining #4.7 billion would be
OL,11,F"confirmed at Budget 2026, in a fair
OL,12,Fand balanced way".
OL,14,FProspective prime minister Mr Burnham
OL,15,Fwas briefed on the Dip before its
OL,16,Fpublication, but it is understood he
OL,17,Fwas not told about the need to find an
OL,18,Fadditional tranche of funding in his
OL,19,Ffirst budget.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782865086
OL,3,CDefence Secretary faces questions on
OL,4,C#4.7bn funding gap left to Andy Burnham
OL,6,FMr Jarvis denied the funding gap was a
OL,7,Fhand grenade for the Makerfield MP `
OL,8,FSir Keir's likely successor ` and his
OL,9,Fnew chancellor, insisting it was
OL,10,F"absolutely the opposite".
OL,12,FHe sidestepped repeated questions on
OL,13,Fwhether it had been made clear to Mr
OL,14,FBurnham that he was being left with a
OL,15,Ffunding gap.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782865086
OL,3,CDefence Secretary faces questions on
OL,4,C#4.7bn funding gap left to Andy Burnham
OL,6,F"Of course we've been talking to Andy
OL,7,FBurnham and his team about this plan,"
OL,8,Fthe new Defence Secretary told BBC
OL,9,FNewsnight, pointing to Sir Keir's
OL,10,Ffocus on a "smooth transition" of
OL,11,Fpower.
OL,13,F"Andy Burnham has an absolute
OL,14,Fcommitment to safeguarding our nation
OL,15,Fand ensuring that we've got the
OL,16,Fresources in place to defend our
OL,17,Fnation in the way that we think is
OL,18,Fnecessary."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@fO]rD@LOUrD@^O]uD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782865086
OL,3,CDefence Secretary faces questions on
OL,4,C#4.7bn funding gap left to Andy Burnham
OL,6,FMr Jarvis told Sky News that given the
OL,7,F"massive expenditure" required to meet
OL,8,Fthe commitment to increasing defence
OL,9,Fspending to 3.5% of gross domestic
OL,10,Fproduct by 2035, it was "not
OL,11,Funreasonable" that "those kinds of
OL,12,Fdecisions are done in the context of a
OL,13,Fspending review".
OL,15,FThe Defence Secretary also said the
OL,16,FDip was "an important signal of our
OL,17,Fintent", as he acknowledged the UK
OL,18,Fwould need to spend more on defence to
OL,19,Fmeet its commitments.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@UO]rD@YOUsD@MO]sD@TOUuD@PO]xD@
OL,26,AIOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782865086
OL,3,CDefence Secretary faces questions on
OL,4,C#4.7bn funding gap left to Andy Burnham
OL,6,FMr Jarvis, who succeeded John Healey
OL,7,Fafter his resignation in June in a row
OL,8,Fover the funding, will likely field
OL,9,Ffurther media questions about the
OL,10,Fcostings at a Wednesday visit to a
OL,11,Fmanufacturing facility.
OL,13,FMs Reeves said the Treasury would
OL,14,Ffocus on finding "efficiencies" and
OL,15,Fcancelling or delaying "lower priority
OL,16,Fprogrammes", while emphasising the
OL,17,FGovernment would not cut day-to-day
OL,18,Fspending to pay for defence.
OL,26,@vD@ROUvD@_O]wD@XOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
