OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782865086
OL,3,CDefence Secretary faces questions on
OL,4,C#4.7bn funding gap left to Andy Burnham
OL,6,FThe plans include billions more for
OL,7,Fthe next generation of stealth jets,
OL,8,Fthe largest ever investment in drone
OL,9,Fwarfare and confirmation that the UK
OL,10,Fwill buy F-35A planes capable of
OL,11,Fcarrying nuclear bombs.
OL,13,FBut older equipment, including two
OL,14,FType 23 frigates and older Chinook and
OL,15,FWildcat helicopters, will be retired.
OL,17,FThe Dip was originally due to be
OL,18,Fpublished last year, but was delayed
OL,19,Fin part due to bitter Whitehall
OL,20,Fwrangling over money.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782865086
OL,3,CDefence Secretary faces questions on
OL,4,C#4.7bn funding gap left to Andy Burnham
OL,6,FThe funding in the Dip comes on top of
OL,7,Fthe #270 billion promised for defence
OL,8,Ffrom 2025/26 to 2028/29.
OL,10,FMax Werner, senior research economist
OL,11,Fat the Institute for Fiscal Studies,
OL,12,Fsaid the decision to leave almost a
OL,13,Fthird of the extra funding to be set
OL,14,Fout at the next budget meant there
OL,15,Fwould be "further impacts on other
OL,16,Fareas of spending, tax or borrowing on
OL,17,Ftop of those set out in today's
OL,18,Fannouncements ` implying one key early
OL,19,Fdecision for the next prime minister".
OL,26,@wD@JOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782865086
OL,3,CDefence Secretary faces questions on
OL,4,C#4.7bn funding gap left to Andy Burnham
OL,6,FWriting in The Telegraph, Mr Jarvis
OL,7,Fsaid: "By the end of the decade,
OL,8,Fspending will be 27% higher in real
OL,9,Fterms than at the start of this
OL,10,Fparliament, with defence's share of
OL,11,FGDP at a 30-year high.
OL,13,F"This sustained increase will
OL,14,Fstrengthen our Armed Forces after a
OL,15,Fperiod of overstretched programmes and
OL,16,Fprovide a clear path to meeting the
OL,17,FUK's Nato commitments while
OL,18,Fmaintaining leadership within the
OL,19,Falliance."
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
